<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Credits — The Studio</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --canvas:   #0f0d0a;
      --canvas2:  #141109;
      --canvas3:  #1c1812;
      --ochre:    #c4933f;
      --ochre-dim:#8a6628;
      --cream:    #f0e6d3;
      --cream-dim:#a89070;
      --stone:    #5a5040;
      --rule:     #231f18;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--canvas);
      color: var(--cream);
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── Back ── */
    .back {
      position: fixed;
      top: 1.75rem;
      left: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .back:hover { color: var(--ochre); }

    /* ── Layout ── */
    .wrap {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 16vh 2rem 10vh;
    }

    /* ── Fade in ── */
    .fade {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease;
    }
    .fade.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* ── Dividers ── */
    .rule-v {
      width: 1px;
      height: 56px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--ochre-dim), transparent);
      margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
    }
    .rule-h {
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--rule);
      margin: 4rem 0;
    }

    /* ── Labels ── */
    .label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 7rem; }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ochre-dim);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .hero-meta {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--stone);
    }
    .hero-meta span { color: var(--ochre-dim); margin: 0 0.6rem; }

    /* ── Two-col credit row ── */
    .credit-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
      gap: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 1.75rem 0;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .credit-row:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }

    .credit-role {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
      padding-top: 3px;
      padding-right: 1.5rem;
    }

    .credit-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .credit-detail {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--cream-dim);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .credit-links { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    .credit-link {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ochre);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ochre-dim);
      padding-bottom: 1px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .credit-link:hover { color: var(--cream); border-color: var(--cream); }

    /* ── Stack table ── */
    .stack-section { margin: 4rem 0; }

    .stack-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .stack-table tr { border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .stack-table tr:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }

    .stack-table td {
      padding: 1.2rem 0;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .stack-table td:first-child {
      width: 140px;
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
      padding-right: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stack-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }

    .stack-note {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--cream-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Commit log ── */
    .commit-log {
      background: var(--canvas2);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .commit-log-header {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    .commit {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .commit:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .commit-hash {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--ochre-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .commit-msg {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--cream-dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Note ── */
    .note-wrap {
      border-left: 1px solid var(--ochre-dim);
      padding-left: 2rem;
      margin: 4rem 0;
    }

    .note-text {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--cream);
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .note-sig {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ochre-dim);
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-text {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--stone);
    }

    .footer-text span { color: var(--ochre-dim); margin: 0 0.5rem; }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .credit-row, .stack-table td:first-child { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .credit-role, .stack-table td:first-child { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; width: auto; }
      .commit { grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <a href="/" class="back">← The Studio</a>

  <div class="wrap">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="fade visible hero">
      <div class="rule-v"></div>
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">A commemorative project<span style="margin:0 1rem;color:#3a3028;">·</span>Built with intent</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">The Studio</h1>
      <p class="hero-meta">
        Edition No. 1 <span>·</span> <%= Date.today.year %> <span>·</span> v1.0.0
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CREDITS -->
    <div class="fade">
      <span class="label">Project Credits</span>

      <div class="credit-row">
        <span class="credit-role">Engineering</span>
        <div>
          <p class="credit-name">Saurabh Kumar</p>
          <p class="credit-detail">
            Software Engineer at Chetu Inc., Noida<br>
            Ruby on Rails · REST APIs · Third-party integrations
          </p>
          <div class="credit-links">
            <a href="https://github.com/Saurabhkr001" class="credit-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/saurabh-kumar-401b42212/" class="credit-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn ↗</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="credit-row">
        <span class="credit-role">For</span>
        <div>
          <p class="credit-name">The Artist</p>
          <p class="credit-detail">
            In his most prolific year yet —<br>
            a space built to catalog, exhibit, and remember.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="credit-row">
        <span class="credit-role">Platform</span>
        <div>
          <p class="credit-name">Ruby on Rails 8</p>
          <p class="credit-detail">The engine beneath the canvas</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-h fade"></div>

    <!-- STACK -->
    <div class="fade stack-section">
      <span class="label">Technical Specifications</span>

      <table class="stack-table">
        <tr>
          <td>Backend</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">Ruby on Rails 8</p>
            <p class="stack-note">MVC architecture · ActiveRecord ORM · Convention over configuration</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Frontend</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">Hotwire — Turbo + Stimulus</p>
            <p class="stack-note">SPA-like navigation without the JavaScript overhead</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Styling</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">Tailwind CSS</p>
            <p class="stack-note">Utility-first · Custom design tokens · Zero dead CSS</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Auth</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">Devise</p>
            <p class="stack-note">Session management · Secure sign-in and sign-out flows</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Storage</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">Active Storage</p>
            <p class="stack-note">Artwork uploads · Avatar management · Variant processing</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Database</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">PostgreSQL</p>
            <p class="stack-note">Relational data · Full-text search · Production-ready</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Typography</td>
          <td>
            <p class="stack-name">Cormorant Garamond + DM Mono</p>
            <p class="stack-note">Display serif paired with a technical monospace — editorial meets precise</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <!-- Commit log easter egg -->
      <div class="commit-log">
        <p class="commit-log-header">Recent commit history</p>

        <div class="commit">
          <span class="commit-hash">a3f91c</span>
          <span class="commit-msg">feat: add custom turbo confirm dialog with ochre aesthetic</span>
        </div>
        <div class="commit">
          <span class="commit-hash">7d2e08</span>
          <span class="commit-msg">feat: portfolio analytics dashboard with chart breakdowns</span>
        </div>
        <div class="commit">
          <span class="commit-hash">c91bb4</span>
          <span class="commit-msg">feat: artwork upload with active storage variant processing</span>
        </div>
        <div class="commit">
          <span class="commit-hash">5f3a12</span>
          <span class="commit-msg">fix: devise sign out now uses turbo delete method correctly</span>
        </div>
        <div class="commit">
          <span class="commit-hash">2b8d77</span>
          <span class="commit-msg">chore: too many commits. worth it.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-h fade"></div>

    <!-- ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS -->
    <div class="fade">
      <span class="label">Special Thanks</span>

      <div class="credit-row">
        <span class="credit-role">Problem solving</span>
        <div>
          <p class="credit-name">Stack Overflow</p>
          <p class="credit-detail">For the answers, and the humbling reminder that someone always asked this before.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="credit-row">
        <span class="credit-role">Infrastructure</span>
        <div>
          <p class="credit-name">Caffeine</p>
          <p class="credit-detail">Silent co-founder. Equity undisclosed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="credit-row">
        <span class="credit-role">Inspiration</span>
        <div>
          <p class="credit-name">The Artist's Work</p>
          <p class="credit-detail">Every design decision started by looking at what the art deserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-h fade"></div>

    <!-- NOTE -->
    <div class="fade">
      <div class="note-wrap">
        <p class="note-text">
          I watched you choose paint when I chose code.
          It turns out we were both trying to build something that lasts.
          This space is yours — to catalog, to exhibit, and to remember.
        </p>
        <p class="note-sig">— Your Annoying Dev Friend</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer class="footer fade">
      <div class="rule-h"></div>
      <p class="footer-text">
        © <%= Date.today.year %> The Studio <span>·</span> Saurabh Kumar <span>·</span> Fin.
      </p>
    </footer>

  </div>

  <script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); });
    }, { threshold: 0.08 });
    document.querySelectorAll('.fade').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>

</body>
</html>